    <h2 class="gallery-title" style="text-align: center;">Winter Landscape</h2>
    <div class="artwork-detail-image-wrap">
      <img src="/images/winter-landscape-sesshu.png" alt="Winter Landscape by Sesshū Tōyō, Muromachi period Japanese ink landscape painting" />
